Site spaces listed on the dashboard should be sorted the same way as it's done in the Space Directory, which seems to sort based on the lowercased space name. See [^spacedirectory-spaces.png].

The dashboard appears to sort based on the default casing of the space name, which can result in unexpected results (see [^dashboard-spaces.png]) because of how the underlying database processes the sort. 

